==Useful Info==
'''Crystal guardians''' are moderately durable [[list of golems|golems]] capable of launching powerful bolts of crystal at anything they encounter. These bolts are unusual in that they can make the target [[fragile]]. Crystal guardians can be found in [[the Vaults]] (usually with a [[peacekeeper]]), the [[Desolation of Salt]], and some [[vault]]s.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Their bolts can make you [[fragile]], so try not to let them hit you when other monsters are around.
*They have infinite [[willpower]] and resistances to most elements. [[Lee's Rapid Deconstruction]] will obliterate them (and anything nearby). Other sorts of [[Earth Magic]] and pure [[Conjurations]] are also effective.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.32]], crystal guardians had [[Crystal Bolt]] instead of [[Crystallizing Shot]].
*Crystal guardians were added in [[0.14]], replacing [[crystal golem]]s.
